citations:
  citation-awoiaf-jenny-of-oldstones:
    source: source-awoiaf
    properties:
      locator: "Jenny of Oldstones"
      accessed: "2026-03-15"
    notes: "Female, Rivermen culture. Alias: Lady Jenny. Spouse: Prince Duncan Targaryen (the Prince of Dragonflies). Claimed descent from kings of the First Men. Duncan married her in 239 AC, giving up his place as heir to the Iron Throne. Brought the Ghost of High Heart (a woods witch) to court, whose prophecy led to the marriage of Aerys and Rhaella. Duncan and Aegon V died in the tragedy at Summerhall in 259 AC; Jenny's fate uncertain."
